trans-unit.source: Represents the geometry of a line.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta la geometria di una riga.

trans-unit.source: To create multiple connected lines, use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.LineSegment> or <xref:System.Windows.Shapes.Polyline> segment with the <xref:System.Windows.Media.PathFigure> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.PathGeometry> classes.
trans-unit.target: Per creare più linee collegate, utilizzare un <xref:System.Windows.Media.LineSegment>o <xref:System.Windows.Shapes.Polyline>segmento con il <xref:System.Windows.Media.PathFigure>e <xref:System.Windows.Media.PathGeometry>classi.</xref:System.Windows.Media.PathGeometry> </xref:System.Windows.Media.PathFigure> </xref:System.Windows.Shapes.Polyline> </xref:System.Windows.Media.LineSegment>

trans-unit.source: **Freezable Features:** Because it inherits from the <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> class, the LineGeometry class provides several special features: LineGeometry objects can be declared as , shared among multiple objects, made read-only to improve performance, cloned, and made thread-safe.
trans-unit.target: **Funzionalità dell'oggetto Freezable:** perché eredita dal <xref:System.Windows.Freezable>(classe), la classe LineGeometry fornisce diverse funzionalità speciali: LineGeometry oggetti è possibile dichiarati come, condivisi tra più oggetti, in sola lettura per migliorare le prestazioni, clonare e resi thread-safe.</xref:System.Windows.Freezable>

trans-unit.source: For more information about the different features provided by <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects, see [Freezable Objects Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Per ulteriori informazioni sulle diverse funzionalità fornite da <xref:System.Windows.Freezable>degli oggetti, vedere [panoramica sugli oggetti Freezable](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Freezable>
